{"tid":957924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭日本封殺 華為在日本5大報登廣告自清","createTime":"2018-12-27T11:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T22:54:16.000Z","uid":28765,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9866f3995b41eace7f8c5300535ea4d4771eabfc","tid":957924,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2018/12/27/php02m5JG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F12%2F27%2Fphp02m5JG.jpg&h=ec1243a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖說：為消除日本消費者和企業對華為的不信任感，華為週四於日本5大全國性報紙刊登廣告，強調嚴格遵守當地法律。（取自華為日本官網）<br />\n<br />\n〔編譯王惠慧／綜合報導〕日本「共同社」報導，日本政府日前決定5G設備將華為排除在採購清單之外，接著日本電信巨頭也跟進；華為週四於日本5大全國性報紙刊登廣告，強調華為嚴格遵守當地法律，希望消除日本消費者和企業對華為的不信任感。<br />\n<br />\n日前日本政府加入「華為包圍網」，決定在5G發展上封殺華為產品，華為週四以華為技術日本株式會社社長王劍峰名義，在日本5家全國性報紙、華為日本官網刊登聲明，強調華為遵守日本及各國的法律規定和國際通訊標準，將資訊安全及隱私保護視為最重要的事項，絕不會讓公司利益凌駕在此之上。<br />\n<br />\n華為在朝日新聞、產經新聞、每日新聞及讀賣新聞刊登半版廣告，在日經新聞刊登全版廣告；另外，富士電視新聞網前報導，相關人士稱日本政府在拆解華為製品後，在硬體中發現多餘零件，華為在聲明中表示，報導完全沒有事實根據。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，華為與多家日本企業關係密切，華為自日企採購零組件的規模，2017年為4900億日圓，並表示2018年採購規模6700億日圓，相當於日本對中國出口額的4%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2654941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2654941&d=hxp9P%2FOyu2kJjEg1%2FFduR5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7755396f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2654941&h=f4e4cecc\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2654941</a>"},{"pid":"4099fb289063aac72c2ad729595cf76b789f526b","tid":957924,"uid":8257,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"此地無銀"},{"pid":"cacf4b6324527a5ada008556326c0b1c5ad3f749","tid":957924,"uid":19437,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:38:13.000Z","msg":"此地無銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be26b24b1ae51df75200b9bc838e0357394c987","tid":957924,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"中國國家情報法第七條"},{"pid":"037840cb03898df1ac64645f973fa05b075d0d7a","tid":957924,"uid":31098,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20101111163058/evchk/images/4/43/11-11-20-36-35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages2.wikia.nocookie.net%2F__cb20101111163058%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F4%2F43%2F11-11-20-36-35.jpg&h=43971988&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af7ef9acb9c5621f654d9c3ad8b5358e12a7cfcb","tid":957924,"uid":13205,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/73996.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F73996.jpg&h=fb2310af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee6e1c033d4ad0e5f2a68260380ecf45296c7dac","tid":957924,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:02:35.000Z","msg":"查出黎係唔清"},{"pid":"1905754105b8a0b22ff8546d94670dbf5d88b8c6","tid":957924,"uid":18955,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:57:12.000Z","msg":"以為日本人on9"},{"pid":"1a3b7a9731da13b026946660172dc0f8db6a5b44","tid":957924,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4099fb289063aac72c2ad729595cf76b789f526b","tid":957924,"uid":8257,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"此地無銀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"點都輸"},{"pid":"a765c59fddfb3123c07986957316fa82feac09a2","tid":957924,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:18:55.000Z","msg":"原來大陸以前既金盾工程即係依家既天網係由華為建構所以華為d產品全部有後門"},{"pid":"e7afb42c3e853957a0a23ea5efdd2a995016b7f5","tid":957924,"uid":220853,